{"tid":731733,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講西醫先進，現代科學知識豐富，現代科技發達，現代醫學倡明的人","createTime":"2018-07-06T12:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T12:57:34.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9d6d1f79b69c9bad79f034fb856c7801e0eda5","tid":731733,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:22:39.000Z","msg":"同吹奏香港係一個先進發達繁榮安定的城市一樣，咁假同咁噁心。<br />\n<br />\n前者無視，大部分現代人，都仲係在痛苦水深火熱之中，科學科技醫學都無法幫助佢地解決問題，仲有一大堆副作用和污染等住你黎食。<br />\n<br />\n後者無視香港一堆社會問題，劏房問題，抑鬱自殺風氣成風。"},{"pid":"998df7ad0ae14f529c5fbf2db642a55968ada063","tid":731733,"uid":51021,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"究竟全盛時期既joe哥可以一日開幾多post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82e52277c20d4118a5a1ee28cf2f0b836de9d3f","tid":731733,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"998df7ad0ae14f529c5fbf2db642a55968ada063","tid":731733,"uid":51021,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:25:13.000Z","msg":"究竟全盛時期既joe哥可以一日開幾多post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a4fd3a642a9d3b03cef6abc00449bd71fd10d3","tid":731733,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dd494681200f2a561d7b94924d279a2cf764f4","tid":731733,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 救世joe"},{"pid":"0